 </b>186.27.<b> Explore options to accede to the Rome Statute of the ICC (Latvia); 
 </b>186.28.<b> Continue its efforts on the ratification of other human rights 
</b></p>
<p><b>instruments and relevant protocols (Mongolia); 
 </b>186.29.<b> Consider signing and ratifying the third OP-CRC-IC (Seychelles); 
