</b></p>
<p><b> </b>186.49.<b> Harmonize the definition of torture contained in the national 
legislation with the requirements of the CAT and ensure that statements 
obtained under duress are not admitted in court (Mexico); 
</b></p>
<p><b> </b>186.50.<b> Continue to improve the legal system, so that it reflects the will 
expressed through the reform of 2012, in order to further ensure the protection 
