in line with its international human rights law obligations (Turkmenistan); 
</b></p>
<p><b> </b>186.55.<b> Follow the approach it took for economic, social and cultural rights 
with respect to civil and political rights, including freedom of religion or belief 
and the right to a fair trial (Slovakia); 
</b></p>
<p><b> </b>186.56.<b> Further guarantee the rights of life, education and health (South 
Africa); 
</b></p>
