special procedures requests (Australia); 
</b></p>
<p><b> </b>186.73.<b> Take the necessary concrete steps to facilitate a visit by the UN High 
Commissioner for Human Rights as soon as possible (Austria); Organize a visit 
of the High Commissioner in the coming future (Slovakia); Facilitate the visits 
of the UN High Commissioner and the special procedures, including to Tibetan 
and Uighur areas (Switzerland); 
</b></p>
<p><b> </b>186.74.<b> Pursue its policies in favour of the vulnerable strata of society (Togo); 
 </b>186.75.<b> Continue to strengthen its efforts to protect the rights of vulnerable 
</b></p>
<p><b>groups with a particular focus on narrowing the gaps between the different 
regions (Bhutan); 
</b></p>
