Plan 2011-2020 set by the State Council in 2011 (United Arab Emirates); 
</b></p>
<p><b> </b>186.80.<b> Continue its effort to promote and protect the rights of children 
including further action against the abduction, maltreatment and abandonment 
of children (Ethiopia); </b></p>


<p><b> </b>186.81.<b> Increase the number of institutions providing professional services 
for the upbringing and protection of orphans, protection of homeless children 
and the rehabilitation of children with disabilities (Kuwait); 
</b></p>
